            <Synopsis>An old priestess visits Mandri at his farm. She is looking for an empty vessel in which to fulfill purpose. &quot;I've heard about you&quot;. Hrkan Lord requires a sacrifice. Kills Gil, and forces Mandri to follow.</Synopsis>
